"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(*)\nFROM account\nJOIN district ON account.district_id = district.district_id\nWHERE district.A2 = 'Litomerice' AND YEAR(account.date) = 1996;\n```\n\nThis SQL query counts the number of accounts opened in the district of Litomerice in the year 1996. It joins the `account` table with the `district` table using the `district_id` foreign key relationship and filters the results based on the district name and the year of the account creation date."